glpng
------------------------------------------
glpng is a small toolkit to make loading PNG image files as an OpenGL texture
as easy as possible.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.7-1
  libGL1-19.1.6-1
  libglpng-devel-1.46-1bl2
  libglpng1-1.46-1bl2
  libpng16-1.6.42-1
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  libGL-devel-19.1.6-1
  libpng-devel-1.6.42-1
  ninja-1.12.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://repo.or.cz/w/glpng.git

Canonical download:
  git://repo.or.cz/glpng.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack glpng-1.46-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./glpng-1.46-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/glpng-1.46-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/glpng-1.46-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libglpng1-1.46-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libglpng-devel-1.46-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(glpng)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/glpng.README
  /usr/share/doc/glpng/glpng.htm

(libglpng1)
  /usr/bin/cygglpng-1.dll

(libglpng-devel)
  /usr/include/GL/glpng.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/glpng/Modules/FindGLPNG.cmake
  /usr/lib/libglpng.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/glpng.pc

------------------

